{
  "stem": "9601.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You can-- you can travel with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was problems, but on the whole-- now I understand those problems.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At that time, you know, it was a minor inconvenience, because I didn't go look for the horse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't go look for the-- for the wagon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My thing was to go have a good time-- either go to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the people used to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Some-- I mean-- I mean, the Christians, the Ukrainians, some thought it was funny-- that it was cute.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And some-- some people thought it's not fair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's not the right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Things like that should not be done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we hardly had any authorities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was only a mayor of the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- most of the problems were religious problems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, you could not go complain that you're being discriminated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could not-- who you gonna go to complain to?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Though the incidents were [? obvious-- ?] you know, hiding the horse-- what are you gonna-- you gonna tell the policeman that-- that-- Besides, you had to go to the county seat to report it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It takes a day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A Jew go to the county seat-- over to the county town-- to the-- to complain about smashed windows?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's only in a Jew's imagination.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It did not happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So people, Jews, did not complain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had to take what they-- what was given.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because if you had to take a day off to go to a little thing called [INAUDIBLE]-- that was the closest official, you know, city, town, or village-- why go?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You're going to be a loser anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When did you first become aware that the War was approaching and the Jewish people were suffering?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941. 1941, I really became aware.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
